node.text:
🏝 VACATION BABY 🏝
.
Earlier this month, I took my first-ever week-long vacation. Tbh, I was an absolute stress case leading up to it because I kept panicking about falling behind in work or letting me team down — or just feeling lazy because I know I push myself to constantly feel productive. At the same time, I knew that taking a break was overdue, I was struggling (even more than usual) to wake up in the mornings bc I was just SO TIRED 😓
.
But, I DID IT! Spent a weekend in Las Vegas for EDC, and then a week in Cancun 💕🏝 When I got back, I felt so stressed about catching up...only to realize that it just took a few extra hours on email one night to feel back on track. The @periodmovement and @juv.consulting teams are so strong, independent, dependable, and bold on their own — and realizing that was not only very humbling, but also made me so proud of both teams, and I feel so excited to dream and do thing bigger this summer with our new interns/associates!!
.
Hoping to vacation again before I go back to Harvard this fall 🦋 any suggestions for affordable/beautiful places to travel?? ✈️
.
pc @shaun__verma
Dress by @rachelpally
U lucky you not run into Mr Stinky on a vacation babe
@annabel_sallinger oooh!! I HAVE NEVER BEEN!! And omg I’ve been wanting to more of Europe. Where in Ireland did u go??? ❤️

@nadyaokamoto I have traveled thru the bottom half of Ireland, and I absolutely adore the Dingle Peninsula. Also, everybody says this, but it’s true, the cliffs of Mohair are a must. 😂.
Aran Islands, are beautiful and lots of fun with great views as well. ♥️
I absolutely love Ireland! You can stay in youth hostels which aren’t too expensive. Absolutely beautiful country. 🇨🇮 I’m glad you had a great vacation!
@hesperkhong OH WHAT!!! Incognito!??? Will definitely try that. I wonder why?
A well deserved vacation!! 🥰❤️ If you turn on incognito mode and use google to search for flights, the tickets are usually cheaper!
Charleston, SC is historic and beautiful, plus they have amazing beaches!
@logssaliga ooh I haven’t heard of that. Will check it out 💕
Scott’s cheap flights and skyscanner shows a lot of great deals too! & you can also look at what the prices will be throughout the month
Thailand 🇹🇭 is affordable . I’m hoping you vacation to Portland / the Northwest. Bend, Oregon is real nice  and a little more space / breathing room than Portland + it has Smith Rock.
@astrid.larson oh!!! Would be a dream to go there ❤️
Everyone deserves a mental health/ de stress break once in a while ! Also suggestion- Punta Cana in the Dominican Republic is beautiful !
@giligy oooh! I’ve only been there once for 24 hours 😂💕
Davis California ;D also just California coast areas in general, lots of variety from north to bay to south. Happy to take youuuu
a very well deserved vacation, i'd say! bali and jamaica are really nice around this time of year 😉
